name: Searchengine.web
description:
This is a very accurate showcase of how a searchengine works. Collect the letters to finish the search and increase your score. But be aware of the five different types of viruses, which are infiltrating the system and hit them with the letters to get rid of them.

(please download and play the windows version if the web version has visual buggs)
